---
title: Moroccan Chickpea, Veggie & Currant Stew with Mash & Almonds
description: Bring the warm Moroccan flavours to your table in the form of a stew packed on top of a blanket of mashed potato. The comforting addition of chickpeas and spices is everything this stew needs to end a long day.

*We’ve replaced the lentils in this recipe with chickpeas due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66f4c797587dccd5cb5f1d5f-b5beb66d.jpeg
